Test Fixtures Directory
======================

This directory contains test fixture data used by the ClawPad integration tests.

Subdirectory purposes:

  setup-state/
    Sample setup-state.json files representing various wizard progress states
    (all-not-started, partially-complete, fully-complete, corrupted).

  uninstall-state/
    Sample uninstall-state.json files for testing resume logic
    (fresh, partially-complete, all-done).

  config/
    Sample openclaw.json and SOUL.md files for config parsing tests.

  env/
    Sample .env files for daemon environment materialization tests.

  node/
    Mock node binary stubs or version output files for installer tests
    (e.g., fake --version output for different semver scenarios).

  keychain/
    Test data for keychain index serialization edge cases
    (empty index, corrupted JSON, duplicate entries).
